ciologists, and criminologists.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aPunishment. 4aMarx. 4aapplied ethics. 4acriminal law. 4acriminology. 4alaw of the penal system. 4alaw. 4aphilosophers. 4aphilosophy of law. 4aphilosophy. 4areform. 4asentencing. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520912311?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520912311423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520912311/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles